| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5291 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 14bfa69d-5d02-516a-a8d9-0bcf4297f6f8"
